                                                                        ‚ö†Ô∏è Gunakan [#id] bukan [#channel] - butuh ID
                                                                        angka!
                                                                    </p>
                                                                    <div
                                                                        class="max-h-40 overflow-y-auto space-y-0 text-xs">
                                                                        <% channels.slice(0, 10).forEach(channel=> { %>
                                                                            <div class="cursor-pointer hover:bg-[#23272f] p-2 rounded transition-colors"
                                                                                onclick="copyToClipboard('[#<%= channel.id %>]', this)">
